# Styles templates (from `styles.json`)

Summarizes **269** stylesheet files: **`.scss`** / **`.css`** (see [`.agents/file-lists/styles.json`](../file-lists/styles.json)). Almost all **`.scss`**; co-located with components, layouts, and pages.

## Inventory snapshot

| Fact | Typical value |
| --- | --- |
| `.scss` vs `.css` | ~99% `.scss` |
| Path depth (median) | 8 segments |
| Common roots | `app/pages` (~66%), `app/components` (~16%), `app/features` (~16%) |
| Largest slice | `app/pages/Result/...` (~55%) |

## Module pattern (next to component)

**`Component.module.scss`**

```scss
.Foo {
  display: flex;

  &_title {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  &___active {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  &___inactive {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
}
```

## BEM (project)

- **Block:** `.Foo`
- **Element:** `&_title` → `.Foo_title`
- **Modifier:** `&___modifier` → `.Foo___modifier` (three underscores in source)

## Global / root

- Root-level **`app/root.css`**, **`app/App.module.scss`** exist for app shell; prefer **feature-local modules** for scoped UI.

